attributes.action: Fund research to cure Lichen Sclerosus in the UK
attributes.background: Lichen Sclerosus is a horrible skin disease that can be alleviated by steroid ointments but no known cure has been found. Often or not it is misdiagnosed and the treatment is started late which can lead to debilitating effects on that person and their mental health.
